    "text": "![](https://www.naukri.com/code360/problems/maximum-value-of-modulus-expression_1215006?interviewProblemRedirection=true&page=2&company%5B%5D=PayPal&sort_entity=recents&sort_order=DESC) ![](https://static.naukimg.com/s/0/0/i/transparentImg.png)\n![Naukri Code 360](https://files.codingninjas.in/new-cn-logos-1-1711622387.svg)\n  * Learn\n\n\n  * Contests & Events\n\n\n  * Interview prep \n\n\n  * Practice\n\n\n  * Resources\n\n\nLogin\nInterview problemsView all problems\nProblem\nSubmissions\nHints & solutions\nDiscuss\n#  Maximum value of modulus expression \nModerate \n![](https://files.codingninjas.in/yellow-spark-22969.svg)\n0/80 \nAverage time to solve is 10m \n[![profile](https://files.codingninjas.in/avatar-1710924338.png)](https://www.naukri.com/code360/profile/91798cca-a5e8-4f45-8427-4494c8daf3a7)\nContributed by \nMutiur \n3 upvotes \nAsked in companies\n![PayPal](https://files.codingninjas.in/company-short-logo-url/675/c432d22f611cbb68026f70492d2f6852.png)![Google](https://files.codingninjas.in/company-short-logo-url/13/4d8a29a3a87330e2b251970b6e6ab4b9.png)![Delhivery](https://files.codingninjas.in/company-short-logo-url/619/117d303896f9082ac8e0d02c6cd26320.png)\n##  Problem statement \nSend feedback \nYou are given two arrays ‘ARR1’ and ‘ARR2’ having equal length ‘N’. Your task is to return the maximum value of the expression:\n**|ARR1[ i ] - ARR1[ j ]| + |ARR2[ i ] - ARR2[ j ]| + |i - j|** , where 0 <= i, j < n and ‘|A|’ represents the absolute (i.e., non-negative) value of ‘A’.\n**Example:** ```\nn = 4, ARR1 = {1, 2, 3, 4}, ARR2 = {-1, 3, 4, 2}\nThe maximum value of the expression is obtained when indexes ‘i = 0’ and ‘j = 3’. After evaluating the expression, we get: \n|ARR1[0] - ARR2[3]| + |ARR2[0] - ARR2[3]| + |0 - 3| => |1 - 4| + |-1 - 2| + |-3| => |-3| + |-3| + 3 => 9\nSo the answer is 9.\n\n```\n\nDetailed explanation  ( Input/output format, Notes, Images ) \n**Input format:** ```\nThe first line of input contains an integer ‘T’ denoting the number of test cases.\nThe first line of each test case contains a single integer ‘N’ denoting the length of array ‘ARR1’ and ‘ARR2’.\nThe second line of each test case contains 'N' space-separated integers denoting the elements of array 'ARR1'.\nThe third line of each test case contains 'N' space-separated integers denoting the elements of array 'ARR2'.\n\n```\n**Output format:** ```\nFor each test case, print a single line containing a single integer denoting the maximum value of the given expression.\nThe output of each test case will be printed in a separate line.\n\n```\n\nNote :\n```\nYou do not need to print anything, it has already been taken care of. Just implement the given function.\n\n```\n\n**Constraints:** ```\n1 <= T <= 100\n1 <= N <= 1000\n-10 ^ 6 <= ARR1[ i ], ARR2[ i ] <= 10 ^ 6\nWhere ‘T’ is the total number of test cases, ‘N’ denotes the length of arrays 'ARR1' & 'ARR2', and ‘ARR1[i]’ & ‘ARR2[i]’ represents the elements in the respective arrays\nTime limit: 1 sec.\n\n```\n\n#### Sample input 1:\n```\n2\n4\n4 3 2 5\n5 -5 1 1\n4\n-2 -3 3 2\n4 4 4 0 \n\n```\n\n#### Sample output 1:\n```\n12\n11\n\n```\n\n#### Explanation of sample input 1:\n```\nTest Case 1:\nThe maximum value of the expression is obtained when indexes ‘i = 0’ and ‘j = 1’. After evaluating the expression, we get: \n|ARR1[0] - ARR2[1]| + |ARR2[0] - ARR2[1]| + |0 - 1| => |4 - 3| + |5 - (-5)| + |-1| => |1| + |10| + 1 => 12\nSo the answer is 12.\nTest Case 2:\nThe maximum value of the expression is obtained when indexes ‘i = 1’ and ‘j = 3’. After evaluating the expression, we get: \n|ARR1[1] - ARR1[3]| + |ARR2[1] - ARR2[3]| + |1 - 3| => |-3 - 2| + |4 - 0| + |-2| => |-5| + |4| + 2 => 11\nSo the answer is 11.\n\n```\n\n#### Sample input 2:\n```\n2\n5\n1 -2 -3 4 5\n-5 -4 -3 2 1\n3\n10 -1 12\n8 0 5\n\n```\n\n#### Sample output 2:\n```\n15\n20\n\n```\n\nC++ (g++ 5.4) \n![Full screen](https://static.naukimg.com/code360/assets/icons/controlled-timer.svg)\n1\n2\n3\n4\n5\n#include<bits/stdc++.h>\nint maxValueOfModulusExpression(vector<int>& arr1, vector<int>& arr2, int n) \n{\n// Write your code here\n}\nEnter to Rename, Shift+Enter to Preview\nConsole \nPrev \nRun  Submit code \nNext \nSettings\nReset Code\nLayouts\nFull Screen Mode\nStart timer\n",
